Let’s keep it real‼️

No one wants to talk about or plan for the day when we’re no longer here‼️

The REALITY is … One day we all will transition from this journey. It is inevitable…

I battled and stalled and procrastinated about my Will + Trust + Estate plan for a looong time‼️

But I finally decided, I owe it to my daughter, my wife, my loved ones to have my affairs in order for when “that day” comes … even though I plan on being around ALOT longer! ( Lord Willing🤞🏾)

Yesterday myself , @mrsjessicabiancia signed the docs‼️

@yourstrulykamara scribbled on a random notepad while we handled the business 😂🤣🤣.

My message to you. Get your affairs in order people. You owe it to your loved ones. This is also a major to step to creating #generationalwealth 💰💰💰
